msgid "No country signal is available on this install. Multi-banner geo-routing will resolve every visitor to \"unknown\" and fall back to your match-all / default banner. The usual fix is to configure %1$s with a free MaxMind GeoLite2 license key. If your site sits behind Cloudflare instead, the %2$s filter is available — note this is a developer code filter, NOT a setting in this screen: a developer adds %3$s in your theme or a code-snippets plugin. Without one of these, the targets you set below have no effect."
